\par Anggrek }{\rtlch \ai\af0\afs22 \ltrch \i\fs22\cf0\lang1040\langfe1033\langnp1040\insrsid9057663\charrsid2061798 Coryanthes}{\rtlch \af0\afs22 \ltrch \fs22\cf0\lang1040\langfe1033\langnp1040\insrsid9057663\charrsid2061798  adalah salah
